data.title: News and features about Lacey chabert
data.meta_description: The Latest Lacey Chabert Breaking News, Comment and Features from Cinemablend
data.text:
Kimberly J. Brown Married Her Halloweentown Co-Star, And Of Course Took Sweet Pics With Best Pal Lacey Chabert On Her Big Day

Halloweentown actress Kimberly J. Brown married former co-star Daniel Kountz, and of course Lacey Chabert was there to celebrate her friend.

Former Halloweentown Disney Channel Star Kimberly J Brown Is Getting Married, And Her Pal Lacey Chabert Sweetly Threw Her Shower

Kimberly J. Brown just got engaged to her Halloweentown co-star, Daniel Kountz, and her pal Lacey Chabert threw her a sweet bridal shower.

Will The Stars Of Hallmark’s The Wedding Veil Reunite For A Third Trilogy? Alison Sweeney Says She’s Down

EXCLUSIVES Alison Sweeney spoke to CinemaBlend about the possibility of a third Wedding Veil trilogy with Lacey Chabert and Autumn Reeser.

Jonathan Bennett Has A Sweet (And Mean Girls-Oriented) Response When Asked What Hallmark Stars He'd Like To Team Up With

Jonathan Bennett's answer for who he'd love to star in a Hallmark movie with is both sweet and, as Mean Girls' Gretchen Wieners would say, so fetch.

'I Think We Share A Special Bond': Mean Girls' Jonathan Bennett Answers Whether He And Lacey Chabert Will Ever Star In A Hallmark Christmas Movie Together

Jonathan Bennett discusses whether he and Mean Girls co-star Lacey Chabert will ever star in a Hallmark Christmas movie together.

Lacey Chabert’s Haul Out The Holly: Lit Up Doesn’t Feel Like A Hallmark Movie For Two Big Reasons, And I'm Sad About It

Lacey Chabert stars in a Hallmark movie sequel, that unfortunately did not live up to the original's hype.

Lacey Chabert On Reuniting With Party Of Five Co-Star For Hallmark Christmas Movie And How She Felt When Filming Ended

Lacey Chabert reunited with Party of Five co-star Scott Wolf for Hallmark's new film A Merry Scottish Christmas and the actress opened up about what the experience was like.

See The Sweet Way Lacey Chabert's Hallmark Co-Stars Supported Her After She Announced An Entirely New Kind Of Project At The Network

Lacey Chabert is set to do a completely new project on the Hallmark Channel, and many of her co-stars and friends shared their support.

After Lacey Chabert’s Merry Scottish Christmas Movie Had A Surprise Cameo, The Two Hallmark Co-Stars Shared A Sweet Exchange

Lacey Chabert's A Merry Scottish Christmas not only included a Party of Five reunion, but one with another Hallmark co-star and the two had a sweet exchange.
